title: Tom Principato - 1999 - Live And Kickin' FLAC
description:
Tom Principato - 1999 - Live And Kickin'

Tom Principato has graced the Washington D.C. area with his extraordinary guitar playing going on 40 years now. Compared to Eric Clapton, a comparison he is extremely proud and honored of, Tom Principato has built himself a huge and somewhat legendary status as one of the best Guitarist in the biz. This 1999 WAMMIE award winner for Best Blues Recording was recorded live in March and April 1999 in Ocean City, Maryland and in performance on Slovenian National Radio. It features John Perry (bass and vocals) and ElTorro Gamble (drums).
